<p class="section-start">Background problem and opportunity</p>
<h3>The capital loan problems, the fast-growth of SME  and fintech industry </h3>
<p>Based on our team research, small medium business (SME) in Indonesia have limited access to get capital loan to grow their business. 
At the same time Bukalapak has approximately 3 million SMEs joining as online sellers, and there was increasing growth of market loan provider because of financial technology (Fintech) that enable easy to comply loan requirements for sellers.
The challenge is..</p>
<p><b>How might we support our sellers get the fund they needed so they can elevate their business?</b></p>
